OL,3,CAttempted murder investigation after
OL,4,Cwoman receives serious facial injuries
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after an incident
OL,8,Fin a Cardiff suburb.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police were called to an
OL,11,Faddress in Aberdulais Crescent Road in
OL,12,FGabalfa at around 4am on Wednesday (27
OL,13,FMay).
OL,15,FA 47-year-old woman was taken to the
OL,16,FUniversity Hospital of Wales where she
OL,17,Fis receiving treatment for serious
OL,18,Ffacial injuries.
