OL,3,CAttempted murder investigation after
OL,4,Cwoman receives serious facial injuries
OL,6,FA 53-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder.JBoth
OL,8,Fare understood to be known to each
OL,9,Fother, South Wales Police said.
OL,11,FA police cordon has been put in place
OL,12,Fas investigations into the incident
OL,13,Fare carried out.
OL,15,FA police spokesperson said: "An
OL,16,Finvestigation has been launched by
OL,17,FSouth Wales Police following an
OL,18,Fincident which took place on
OL,19,FAberdulais Crescent, Gabalfa at
OL,20,Fapproximately 4am today (Wednesday,
OL,21,FMay 27).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
