PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779981070
OL,3,CAttempted murder investigation after
OL,4,Cwoman receives serious facial injuries
OL,6,F"A 53-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder. The
OL,8,Fvictim - a 47-year-old woman - is
OL,9,Fcurrently at the University Hospital
OL,10,Fof Wales where she is receiving
OL,11,Ftreatment for serious facial injuries.
OL,13,F"Both are understood to be known to
OL,14,Feach other. A police cordon remains in
OL,15,Fplace at the scene of the incident."
OL,17,FDetective Inspector Phillip Marchant,
OL,18,Fmade a plea for people to come forward
OL,19,Fwith relevant dash cam footage.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
