PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779981070
OL,3,CAttempted murder investigation after
OL,4,Cwoman receives serious facial injuries
OL,6,FHe said: "I am urging anyone who may
OL,7,Fhave been driving through the area at
OL,8,Fthe time, and local residents, to
OL,9,Fcheck dash cams or ring doorbell
OL,10,Fcameras for anything which may be
OL,11,Frelevant to our investigation.
OL,13,F"Officers are currently in the area to
OL,14,Freassure residents and carry out house
OL,15,Fto house enquiries.
OL,17,F"We have arrested a man in connection
OL,18,Fwith the incident and are not looking
OL,19,Ffor anybody else at this time."
